R.F. Sahlberg, 1844: 37. Type locality: &quot;monte Morikan [Okhotsk, Khabarovsk Kray, Russia]&quot; (original citation). Lectotype (♀), designated by Bousquet (1999: 191), in ZMH.
</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="545" pageNumber="546">
<taxonomicName authorityName="J. Sahlberg" authorityYear="1885" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Feronia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Coleoptera" pageId="545" pageNumber="546" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="thulensis">Feronia thulensis</taxonomicName>
